{"tid":1313324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"上水人有嘢講","createTime":"2019-07-13T17:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T18:14:45.000Z","uid":169043,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24f6b826926809d39873b2c712d7374c8d6f7998","tid":1313324,"uid":169043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"今日遊行同衝突都一直喺度，本質光復上水係為咗重奪社區 ；去為香港人發聲。但係上水問題嘅根本係來自政權嘅不公政策同埋不民主的體制。<br />\n<br />\n尤其是有留守嘅想法之前，一定要諗升級行動對大局的影響。要反問自己究竟升級行動嘅焦點同目的喺邊度呢？和平遊行雖然沒用，但係仲有好多戰術考慮因素。我真係唔忍心再見到自己人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n消耗緊狗嘅體力嘅同時，其實都係消耗緊好多前線手足同大家嘅意志。其實行一日真係好撚攰，聽日仲有一場沙田。尤其是cctvb,又可以繼續爭取時間扭曲事實。所以我地認真思考priorities.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但最後最後，好想衷心多謝各位手足。我竟然可以喺北區見到好多金鐘曾經見到嘅影子。多謝你哋。"},{"pid":"c739a7e1bd3fb6f7da9543747c039eb4283b4706","tid":1313324,"uid":169043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d22f8b1c73da8b7110b66c10db506e189231ca0a","tid":1313324,"uid":169043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4a72a4d51e02ea0fc861fa1251c995e3f2cd3f7c","tid":1313324,"uid":169043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cfab5074f4f721b5efc5ec9ea867eaeaa7ed177b","tid":1313324,"uid":169043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd7a1346c74c4b0c48fed83f93e932081dc77b4f","tid":1313324,"uid":59965,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:46:32.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬今日入黎上水嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然好攰 但沙田要人！！！<br />\n沙田有預感會打得更激 <br />\n人多先保得住手足啊！！！"},{"pid":"a4beb5fccf9ea454f9e49241d2371068f7d79814","tid":1313324,"uid":169043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2c294022588a12511c069d36376e01b35309cf02","tid":1313324,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3758f9af0055d09895a9eb2c4ba9bf95eee80a1d","tid":1313324,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0892ffb93e001f179c0662094baf96476e903c19","tid":1313324,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:14:45.000Z","msg":"聽日沙田見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}